title: Package Receiving, Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent, Dog Park
posting_body: ['1304 Bruskrud Road, Everett, WA 98208', 'Located in the Twin Creeks neighborhood of Everett, Washington, Tessera Apartments is less than 10 minutes from Boeing and the Everett Naval Station.', 'With downtown Everett located just 6 miles north and with easy access to I-5, no matter where your traveling, it will be a breeze.', 'If shopping is what your looking for, the Everett mall is just a short drive down the road where you can find a variety of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options.', 'At the community, residents enjoy surfing the web using the free wifi in the business center, or getting their workout on in our state-of-the-art fitness center.', 'With all these conveniences it’s easy to see Tessera is right where you want to be!', 'Apartment Features:', 'Newly Renovated Interiors', 'Patio/Deck', 'Pantry Closet in Select Units', 'High Ceilings', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Large Walk-In Closets', 'Community Features:', 'Business Center', 'Dog Park', 'Guest Parking', 'Fitness Center', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Package Receiving', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!', 'Carports are available for additional cost.']
